00:00:42.299 --> 00:00:46.259
Seeing the faces and hearing the stories of our brothers and sisters around the globe

00:00:46.259 --> 00:00:52.259
has given this great crowd reassurance of what a close family we are, all taking part

00:00:52.259 --> 00:00:55.859
in the same work wherever we live.

00:00:55.859 --> 00:00:59.619
What are your favorite moments from JW Broadcasting?

00:00:59.619 --> 00:01:03.979
Perhaps the following compilation from the last two years will help remind you.

