00:01:51.650 --> 00:01:56.730
One of the brothers are made to ask me, if I prove from the Bible that something you believe

00:01:56.730 --> 00:01:59.730
is incorrect, what will you do?

00:01:59.730 --> 00:02:01.769
I say, then I will become a witness.

00:02:01.769 --> 00:02:06.650
I always said no.

00:02:06.650 --> 00:02:12.409
I said, quick being a stubborn mule, at least read it.

00:02:12.409 --> 00:02:16.090
He says, do you know what I was just doing?

00:02:16.090 --> 00:02:18.090
No.

00:02:18.090 --> 00:02:23.990
I was on my knees and tears.

00:02:23.990 --> 00:02:27.870
I was begging God to send somebody.

00:02:27.870 --> 00:02:32.270
After studying with six different elders, I realized that it's not one person that

00:02:32.270 --> 00:02:37.349
changes everybody, but everybody that changes one person.

00:02:37.349 --> 00:02:42.909
And remember that one day years ago, we were trying to understand the Bible without having

00:02:42.909 --> 00:02:45.030
any chance to understand it.

00:02:45.030 --> 00:02:47.710
And now we are sitting there, Jova's witnesses.

00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:55.509
What a privilege we have to know and use the personal name of our loving Father, Jova.

00:02:55.509 --> 00:03:03.909
Jesus tells us that no one can come to the Father unless Jova draws that person.

00:03:03.909 --> 00:03:10.590
What he saw, I don't know, but I'm deeply appreciative.

00:03:10.590 --> 00:03:14.430
There's nothing here on this earth to compare with God's organization.

00:03:14.430 --> 00:03:19.710
There's never been anything even back in Bible times to compare with what Jova has

00:03:19.710 --> 00:03:21.509
now and what he's doing now.

00:03:21.509 --> 00:03:30.550
I found people that I was looking for, people without prejudice, without pride, different

00:03:30.550 --> 00:03:39.629
nationalities, and that was like taking a deep breath of hope.

00:03:39.629 --> 00:03:45.229
I see that Satan's methods have not changed, but it is really encouraging to remember that

00:03:45.229 --> 00:03:47.949
Jova also has not changed.

00:03:47.949 --> 00:03:55.169
He defended and protected his people in the past, and he will do the same today.

00:03:55.169 --> 00:03:59.569
