00:04:18.470 --> 00:04:23.629
I pray to Jova not to remove this challenges, but to give me the strength to overcome this

00:04:23.629 --> 00:04:25.110
challenges.

00:04:25.110 --> 00:04:29.430
We also remember that anyone can complain about an imperfect process.

00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:30.430
That's easy to do.

00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:31.709
All of us can do that.

00:04:31.709 --> 00:04:36.509
But the real gem of a person, the one that can be used the most by Jova is the one who

00:04:36.509 --> 00:04:42.230
